# matplotlib.axis.XAxis.set_ticks_position

XAxis.set_ticks_position(position)[source]

    
Set the ticks position.

Parameters

    
position{'top', 'bottom', 'both', 'default', 'none'}

    
'both' sets the ticks to appear on both positions, but does not change the
tick labels. 'default' resets the tick positions to the default: ticks on both
positions, labels at bottom. 'none' can be used if you don't want any ticks.
'none' and 'both' affect only the ticks, not the labels.
